member.name: F:Gw2Sharp.ChatLinks.Internal.BuildChatLinkStruct.Specialization1TraitIndices
member.summary: The first specialization trait indices in little endian format.
member.remarks:
There are 3 trait indices, and each trait index consumes 2 bits and is 0-indexed. There is a 2 bit padding at the end to fill 1 byte.
The following values are possible: 0 = no trait selected. 1 = top trait selected (matches trait index 0, 3, 6 on ). 2 = middle trait selected (matches trait index 1, 4, 7 on ). 3 = bottom trait selected (matches trait index 2, 5, 8 on ).
